Description:
    Generates a custom pipe for I18nOnSteroids with boilerplate code.

Example:
    rails generate i18n_pipe my_custom

    This will create:
        app/pipes/my_custom_pipe.rb
        config/initializers/i18n_on_steroids.rb (if not exists)

    And register the pipe in the initializer.

Options:
    --namespace=NAMESPACE
        Organize pipe under a namespace (e.g., datetime, money, text)

        Example:
            rails generate i18n_pipe format --namespace=datetime

        Usage in translations:
            ${date | datetime.format: %Y-%m-%d}

    --description=DESC
        Add a custom description for the pipe

        Example:
            rails generate i18n_pipe reverse --description="Reverses a string"

Complete Examples:
    rails generate i18n_pipe currency_symbol
    rails generate i18n_pipe format --namespace=datetime
    rails generate i18n_pipe humanize_bytes --namespace=file --description="Converts bytes to human readable format"
